@startuml
title PayMate Project: RAD Model Application

skinparam activity {
    BackgroundColor #FFF0E6
    BorderColor #FF8C00
    ArrowColor #333
    FontName Inter
    FontSize 14
}
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #F5F5F5
    BorderColor #888
    FontName Inter
    FontSize 12
}

start

:Requirements Planning;
note right
    - High-level goals are defined.
    - **PayMate Example:** "Build a digital
      payment app with AI features."
    - Scope is kept flexible.
end note

repeat
    :User Design & Prototyping;
    note left
        **Rapid Prototyping Cycle**
        - UI is built with ShadCN components.
        - AI flows are created with Genkit.
        - **Example:** A functional Transfer page
          prototype is built immediately.
    end note

    :User Review & Feedback;
    note right
        - User interacts with the live prototype.
        - Feedback is given directly.
        - **Example:** "This is great, but can you
          also add a QR code upload button?"
    end note

    :Construction & Refinement;
    note left
        - Prototype is refined based on feedback.
        - The working model is updated.
        - Low-level coding and integration.
    end note

repeat while (User requests more changes?) is (yes)
-> (no);

:Cutover (Deployment);
note right
    - Final system is deployed.
    - User training and handoff.
    - PayMate app is released.
end note

stop
@enduml
